Tag: spurious-fields-in-upstream-signature
Severity: wishlist
Certainty: certain
Check: upstream-signature
Info: The packaging includes a detached upstream signature file that contains
 spurious fields like <tt>Comment:</tt> or <tt>Version:</tt>. They are
 sometimes added by <tt>gpg --enarmor</tt>.
 .
 Please generate the signature with <tt>gpg --armor --detach-sig</tt> instead.

